### ==========================================
### 1. Existing Financial Tracker API (Port 3000)
### ==========================================

### Get All Expenses
GET http://localhost:3000/api/expenses HTTP/1.1

###

### Create an Expense
POST http://localhost:3000/api/expenses HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 25.5,
  "date": "2026-07-19",
  "tags": ["food", "personal"],
  "description": "Lunch",
  "account": "Credit card",
  "verified": false
}

###

### Update an Expense (Replace :id with a valid UUID from GET /api/expenses)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/expenses/e3365038-5de1-4dc9-bb34-dd84931c143f HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Lunch at REST API Cafe",
  "verified": true
}

###

### Delete an Expense (Replace :id with a valid UUID from GET /api/expenses)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/expenses/replace-with-actual-uuid HTTP/1.1

###

### Get All Incomes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/incomes HTTP/1.1

###

### Create an Income
POST http://localhost:3000/api/incomes HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1200,
  "date": "2026-07-19",
  "tags": ["salary"],
  "description": "Payroll",
  "account": "Checking"
}

###

### Update an Income (Replace :id with a valid UUID from GET /api/incomes)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/incomes/replace-with-actual-uuid HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1250,
  "description": "Monthly Payroll + Bonus"
}

###

### Delete an Income (Replace :id with a valid UUID from GET /api/incomes)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/incomes/replace-with-actual-uuid HTTP/1.1

###

### Get Reports
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reports HTTP/1.1

###

### Get Tags List
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tags HTTP/1.1


### ==========================================
### 2. New LLM Agent Gateway API (Port 3001)
### ==========================================

### Send Natural Language Message to LLM Gateway (Creates an Expense)
POST http://localhost:3001/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "two days ago I bought a laptop with my credit card for a thousand"
}

###

### Send Natural Language Message (Creates an Income)
POST http://localhost:3001/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Yesterday I received a bonus from work of five hundred dollars into my Savings account"
}

###

### Test Connectivity to LLM Gateway
GET http://localhost:3001/test HTTP/1.1